text:
Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me VICTON's Subin and Heochan look handsome in individual teasers for their comeback By beansss 43 minutes ago 1,981 318 4 0 SEE ALSO: VICTON drop video teasers of Hanse and Byungchan for 'EYEZ EYEZ' 
The two look handsome in a set of individual teaser images, going from colored in a warmly lit setting to colder in a black and white photo. Their video teasers also indicate slightly different moods - Subin's teaser is more mellow, while in Heochan's teaser, he shows off crisp dance moves. 
Keep an eye out for more of VICTION's teasers, leading up to their full comeback with 2nd mini album ' Ready ' and title track " Eyez Eyez " on March 2! YOU MAY LIKE GET AKP IN YOUR INBOX! ..or follow allkpop to stay updated: Tags:
